This repository contains unofficial compatibility modifications for
Soul-AILab/SoulX-Singer. The original project and its copyright notices are
available at https://github.com/Soul-AILab/SoulX-Singer.

Modified areas are distributed as the unified patch in
patches/soulx-singer-amd-windows.patch. The changes add Windows AMD ROCm
single-GPU compatibility, progress reporting, local-path SVC API integration,
and bounded inference-session retention.
